{"tid":204313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片]思古井親身上耶教異聞錄及教會趕客實錄","createTime":"2017-04-17T02:48:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T20:02:08.000Z","uid":80991,"like":60,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9996e1eb637222e2939d44c203ffeae6e7dd8680","tid":204313,"uid":80991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T02:48:07.000Z","msg":"我呢幾日親身上咗耶教異聞錄 教會趕客實錄,做嘉賓。<br />\n去同大家分享自己嘅事<br />\n<br />\n雖然我係上咗兩個節目<br />\n但係我係兩個節目入邊講嘅嘢係好唔同,咁當然都係圍繞住自己嗰件事啦。<br />\n不過我可以同大家保證嘅係重複嘅部份係比較少。<br />\n同埋我上節目講嘅嘢，全部之前上網都係未講過,係一啲新嘅嘢。<br />\n<br />\n同埋我既然選擇以真面目公開見人,我亦都已經有個心理準備會俾大家評頭品足,不過無論點都好我希望大家有時間得閒嘅話就可以聽下。<br />\n<br />\n17年04月16日｜教會趕客實錄 (第1節) 現代獵巫行動-博恩浸信會逼害前信徒，思古井控訴/環保生活有辦法<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=36E62boLoyU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D36E62boLoyU&d=qJ6fIGaH6M%2FMetNSomypD54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=2ce87fbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=36E62boLoyU</a><br />\n<br />\n教會趕客實錄 (第2節) 揭穿聖女葉希臨真面目，如何誣衊思古井<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TBh_qJVyF3A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTBh_qJVyF3A&d=qJ6fIGaH6M%2FMetNSomypD54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=49280a6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TBh_qJVyF3A</a><br />\n<br />\n教會趕客實錄 (第3節) 思古井之一念無明，揭破葉希臨蛇蠍心腸，依然抹黑思古井<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tBO9wjNrOFM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtBO9wjNrOFM&d=qJ6fIGaH6M%2FMetNSomypD54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=315d20d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tBO9wjNrOFM</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於耶教異聞錄,就會係今晚 晚上9點播出<br />\n[url<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/4.0/live.php][/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2F4.0%2Flive.php%5D%5B%2Furl%5D&d=qJ6fIGaH6M%2FMetNSomypD54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=b93b07be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/4.0/live.php][/url]</a><br />\n<br />\n希望各位睇完聽完之後可以,分享出去比更加多人知道,係香港有一個年青比浸信會迫害到連前途都冇埋。<br />\n<br />\n無論係任何人,只要大家想聯絡我,大家都可以whatsapp我<br />\n98253639"},{"pid":"778c4d72eff07c847ad554336247f8e02d0292f4","tid":204313,"uid":80991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T02:49:45.000Z","msg":"至於耶教異聞錄,就會係今晚 晚上9點播出<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/4.0/live.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2F4.0%2Flive.php&d=qJ6fIGaH6M%2FMetNSomypD54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=88ef4ea8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/4.0/live.php</a>"},{"pid":"3890f8802dd78e1b159ef584af5cce5d3ef14327","tid":204313,"uid":80991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T03:07:26.000Z","msg":"LM 左先"},{"pid":"e4a74b527a2c8436e54eda2c454b1de8268be761","tid":204313,"uid":35507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T03:09:09.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"b9905ffa2427f2105a44bf36245277a120309406","tid":204313,"uid":80991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T03:40:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aeee6b4c8f6d7bead810e197b3700bfb8c6437b0","tid":204313,"uid":20554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T03:44:04.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n勇氣可加<br />\n自殺之說不攻自破"},{"pid":"5bd8514c124a34c25cb42748c4b6b7b0d444d79c","tid":204313,"uid":35730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T03:44:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7296c11dd73f3d86b7e8cd983807049fbddf6658","tid":204313,"uid":80991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T03:48:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推<br />\n勇氣可加<br />\n自殺之說不攻自破</blockquote><br />\n多謝"},{"pid":"2895b7fe2c186cae2b6a099d29fdc3ff995c1ae4","tid":204313,"uid":80991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"